OL,3,CChildren's hospice celebrates 25th
OL,4,Canniversary
OL,6,FDescribed as a extraordinary, a
OL,7,Fhospice on the outskirts of Cardiff
OL,8,Fhas celebrated a momentous milestone
OL,9,Fin its history.
OL,11,FTy Hafan Hospice, in Sully, marked 25
OL,12,Fyears since its doors first opening to
OL,13,Fchildren with life-shortening
OL,14,Fillnesses.
OL,16,FIt has supported more than a thousand
OL,17,Ffamilies through some of their most
OL,18,Fdifficult times, many of whom were at
OL,19,Fthe hospice to celebrate the important
OL,20,Fday.
