OL,6,FJohn Weaver whose daughter was one of
OL,7,Fthe first children cared for at the
OL,8,Fhospice said, "it is down to love, and
OL,9,Fthat is what Ty Hafan is all about".
OL,11,FFor parents who are told their
OL,12,Fchildren have a life-limiting illness,
OL,13,Fthere can often seem like there is
OL,14,Flittle hope.
OL,16,F25 years ago, Ty Hafan Hospice opened
OL,17,Fits doors for the first time in the
OL,18,Fhope of providing care and support to
OL,19,Fthose children and their loved ones.
