OL,3,CChildren's hospice celebrates 25th
OL,4,Canniversary
OL,6,FSince then, it has supported more than
OL,7,F1,100 young people, by providing
OL,8,Fspecialist support as well as a place
OL,9,Fto feel safe.
OL,11,FLiz and John Weaver's daughter, Emily,
OL,12,Fwas the first of those thousands of
OL,13,Fchildren to benefit from the charity's
OL,14,Fservices, aged 12.
OL,16,FMore than two decades later, Emily,
OL,17,F37, and her parents returned to mark
OL,18,Fthe important day. Liz said Ty Hafan
OL,19,F"was an absolute lifeline".
