OL,6,F"Ty Hafan was not what I expected",
OL,7,Fshe said, "it was such a happy fun
OL,8,Fplace to be, the staff are amazing and
OL,9,FEmily had an absolute every time she
OL,10,Fvisited here."
OL,12,F"When surgery, medication and
OL,13,Ftreatment is no longer any use, it is
OL,14,Fdown to love and that's what Ty Hafan
OL,15,Fis all about", said Emily's dad, John.
OL,17,FThe hospice would never had reached
OL,18,Fthis landmark day without the support
OL,19,Fof donations from the public, said
OL,20,FMaria Timon Samra, the hospice's CEO.
