OL,6,F"Down through the years, the people of
OL,7,FWales have been behind us all the way,
OL,8,Fwe're so eternally grateful for that
OL,9,Fas we know the families are as well",
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FLooking forward to another two
OL,13,Fdecades, Maria said, "we really want
OL,14,Fto do more for children and families
OL,15,Fto make their lives as good as they
OL,16,Fpossibly can be.
OL,18,F"Let's hope in 25 years, someone
OL,19,Flooking back will say we've managed to
OL,20,Fachieve that."
